'''Tamsmunt tamɣribit n urzzu d umrara adlsan''' nɣ '''Agraw amɣribi n usiggl d isnfiln n tussna''' (s taserɣint: الجمعية المغربية للبحث والتبادل الثقافي) nɣ '''Agraw n Lmeɣrib ɣ isiggel d isnifilen n tawessna'''<ref>Ɣikad a's tt-inn-ikka ittyura isem-nnes ɣ ulugu-nnes akkʷ izwaren.</ref> (s tefṛansist: ''Association marocaine de recherche et d'échange culturels'', s uzegzel AMREC). Tga [[tamsmunt]] tamzwarut isawwaln f [[izrfan]] n ufgan d tutlayt Tamaziɣt g Lmɣrib.
Tamsmunt ad ttyuskar g usggas u 1967 f ufus n mnnaw ddakatiṛa d [[Aslmad|islmadn]] isddawin (n tasddawit) g Rrbaṭ.

Tlul ɣ tamdint n rbaṭ ɣ was 10 nuwanbir 1967 {{Asggas amaziɣ|28 ktubr 2917}}, tsmun yat trabbut n imḥdarn imaziɣn ɣi illa Ɛli Azayku, Brahim Axiat, Ahmed Bukus, Abdelfadl Lɣwali, Abdellaḥ Bunfur, Ahmed Akuawu, Omar  Lxalfawi, Ali  Ljawi. Nzzḍar anini mas mass [[Brahim Axyyaṭ]] nttan ad igan Babas n Tamsmunt ad s twisi n Mass [[Ahmed Bukus|Aḥmad Bukus]].

G tizwiri, tamsmunt ur dars ḥtta kan [[Awngim asrtan|uwngim asrtan]], ar tsuggur ɣar atsmun tiɣbula f tadlsa tamaziɣt fknas ssiɛr g ugnsu n Lmɣrib. Nzzḍar anini mas tarabbut ad tga ɣu umzwaru ntuwuriwi nes ad mallan slmdn isbbabn d ix ddamn ad taran da adqran. Macc, ḍart 1967 tamsmunt kcmn sers tugt n imɣnasn, zund imɣnasn n [[iẓẓlmḍ]], nutni ad ayullin, asin [[awngim amaziɣ]] bac ad ikcem tasertit seg waggur kullu ymqqurn.
